This version of the game is designed to manage half of the game. The half of the game that deals with players choosing there defenses.
In the next version of the game we are planning to introduce combat between the USA and Russia as well as options for more players.
We are also planning on adding graphics in the next version as well.

The Program works by using 4 different programs. Each program is represented by what they are used to create.
The four programs are City, Defense, Player, and Weapon.
Weapons is used to get information for weapons.
Defenses works to show how defenses are used and what they can target
Player shows what commands in order to add defenses as well as weapons. It even allows
City is used to control the different cities and control populations.

